Before any subcommand dispatches, three uniform checks run: (1) global_flag_stripping removes --json/--no-color/--color= from args; (2) help_flag intercepts cmd --help/-h and returns the command's usage text; (3) unknown_flag_rejection rejects any unrecognized --flag or -x. These checks run for EVERY subcommand including those that take no arguments. See <ref spec="cli.unknown_flag_rejection">unknown flag rejection</ref>.